Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:04.00,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go over safety before we hit the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:07.53,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If you have a fever, haven't slept,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:09.13,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my eyes meet\Nwith my classmate's, Sugawara-kun's,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:10.80,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}or if haven't had breakfast, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.21,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,a lot during swimming class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.73,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:17.59,sign_1743_7_Gaze,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,650)}Gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:16.70,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Was he looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:21.01,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, there's no way\Nhe would be looking at {\i0}me{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.22,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but glance at Takano
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.52,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,in her swimsuit during swimming class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:28.82,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes even met just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:30.52,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stop, or she'll get creeped—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.31,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do warm-up exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:35.06,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.62,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:40.24,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,five, six, seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:44.25,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But why do Sugawara-kun's and my eyes meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.53,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he was looking at someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.19,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, our eyes keep meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.90,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She knows I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:57.63,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should say hi rather than\Npretend nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.60,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who he just waved to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.48,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like anyone reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.98,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.98,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.65,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.37,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Should I apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.50,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But then I should do it during break
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.90,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he's looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.83,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for reacting as if he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.12,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to get more awkward\Nas time passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.00,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I should be casual about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:34.18,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll ask him who he's looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.54,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All right, jump in in order, on my mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry about what's been happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:45.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not on purpose,\Nbut I kept glancing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for interrupting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Interrupting what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking at\Nsomeone else, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The girl beside me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You, Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:06.78,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.54,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What did Sugawara-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.82,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takano?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.92,Default,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.15,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun was watching me this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.08,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.00,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have that nice of a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.72,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.04,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.31,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my heart racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sugawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:35.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was looking at you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.10,Default,Guyoda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Goda, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.32,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.45,Default,Guyoda,0000,0000,0000,,Should I pass that on to Sugawara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.96,sign_5548_65_The_End,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:57.46,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been awkward ever since\NI confessed to the guy I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.95,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can give up dating him, but I want\Nto at least go back to being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:05.97,sign_5772_68_Square_One,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,650)}Square One
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.42,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No, I want to date him if I can, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.74,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a month since Kanda confessed\Nto me. I haven't been able to reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.48,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She avoids me when I try to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.99,sign_6174_72_It_hasn_t_bother,Text,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't bothered me. \N\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.71,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is her only reply to my message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.61,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would I just be annoying if I kept trying\Nto talk when she doesn't want me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.90,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too late for me to confess again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.40,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize to Takase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.71,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize and make things normal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.03,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.97,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:53.48,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.73,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How did I talk to Takase before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.32,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.31,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Something's different again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.23,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Cras—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:02.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.71,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I misspoke! Crap, that was embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:27.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning to apologize,\Nbut I couldn't find the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:30.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I've been meaning to say something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:31.84,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.34,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell him honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:37.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:39.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:45.51,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that sounded like\NI don't like him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:50.28,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe it's easier to make up if I act\Nlike I don't have feelings for him anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You really don't care anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.87,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is he asking because he's relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.21,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Or because he's disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.10,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If there's still a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-If it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's be friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.23,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.01,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.74,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I should have confessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.74,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was being friend-zoned all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.18,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we made up,\Nbut now I have mixed feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can stop avoiding me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:52.04,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend and I kissed for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.44,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But it was so sudden, I choked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:01.77,sign_9988_130_Once_More,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,650)}Once More
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.45,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who chokes on their first kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.11,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I want to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.65,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.24,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kamine's been weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.78,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she wants to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.95,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about that kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.24,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is she pissed that I did it out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:19.25,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Was it too soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.25,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Goda-kun\Nisn't going to do it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.94,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.67,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.58,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I never had her permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.01,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It must have bothered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.91,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be the one to ask, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.51,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he'll do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.52,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll quit doing that kind of thing\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Goda-kun, there's no one\Nat the park today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make you think of that kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go somewhere else, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if it bothers you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:05.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to try again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:19.25,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like he's going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.31,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the mood's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.95,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty wary of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.81,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be careful\Nso she doesn't think I'm a player.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,M-Man, I'm getting sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:38.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:40.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.08,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"There"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.90,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sleeping in his lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.34,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's going to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.37,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe this will get him in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.84,sign_12764_177_Zzz___,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,1)}Zzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.24,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.81,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.53,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been tired from club work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.85,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to touch your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.67,sign_13559_188_The_End,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:34.99,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Minagawa-san, the student president,\Nsays she likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:37.63,sign_13733_190_Like,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}Like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:41.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Minagawa-san, are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:43.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"No"? So you were kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I wasn't {\i1}kidding{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't shown you {\i1}serious{\i0} power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like this sort of thing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what's your usual "like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My usual is "like" as in,\N"You're so cute, Furuya-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was "like" as in,\N"You're so cute when you're angry."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to answer\Nwhen you act like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to give me an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, I don't like\Nletting it drag on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll listen seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:34.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't give an answer\Nif you aren't serious about liking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle my serious "like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll let you hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're already making a joke out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:07.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was an "I like your serious face, too"\Nkind of "like."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.11,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so, too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:23.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,None of them really clicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can't express\Nmy serious "like" in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are they closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open them until I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.24,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.59,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.27,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't even dating yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.16,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, so why don't I just go out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:01.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did you feel my serious "like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What part of that was serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You used your fingers\Nto pretend you were kissing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.49,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that was my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:17.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell if that was my fingers\Nor if I was serious, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Lovers.
